cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO 

This paper focuses on analyzing referential expressions in images, which involves both natural language processing and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). However, since the paper also presents a novel architecture that learns linguistic analysis and visual inference end-to-end, it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, since the approach involves deep learning, it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.RO (Robotics).
